<bold>Primary outcome:</bold> Expression of mRNA for &#x003b1;-SMA to establish an effective dose of adalimumab for downregulation of the myofibroblast phenotype. </p><p>
<bold>Secondary outcomes:</bold> Expression of mRNA for COL-1A1, COL-3A1 and cadherin 11, and levels of &#x003b1;-SMA protein to determine the effectiveness of adalimumab for myofibroblast inhibition. Nodule hardness and ultrasound image of nodule dimensions/size. Adverse event assessment using visual inspection of injection site, surgery site and laboratory reports.</p><p>
<bold>Tertiary outcomes:</bold> Circulating levels of adalimumab and antibodies to adalimumab. The injection experience will be rated by the participant and the injection site assessed for local adverse events.</p><p>
