<bold>Secondary outcomes:</bold> Nodule dimensions/area (determined by ultrasound imaging), range of motion of the affected digit, grip strength, patient reported outcome measures of hand function, progression to surgery of the digit being assessed, injection experience and adverse events.</p><p>
<bold>Tertiary outcomes:</bold> Circulating levels of adalimumab, and antibodies to adalimumab. Healthcare resource use and health-related quality of life.</p><p>
