<article-title>Dupuytren Contracture Recurrence Following Treatment With Collagenase Clostridium histolyticum (CORDLESS [Collagenase Option for Reduction of Dupuytren Long-Term Evaluation of Safety Study]): 5-Year Data.</article-title>
<source><italic>J Hand Surg Am</italic></source>.<year>2015</year>;<volume>40</volume>(<issue>8</issue>) :
